    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with hematological malignancy

          -  Age&lt;55 years

          -  HCT-CI score â‰¥ 3 or non-eligible for myeloablative regimen

          -  Patients without a matched related donor

          -  Patients eligible for an allogeneic HSCT from an alternative donor

          -  Able to comply with the protocol

          -  Written informed consent

          -  Patient affiliated to the national &quot;Social Security&quot; regimen or beneficiary of this
